<h1>Josh Pitzalis</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://www.joshpitzalis.com/now/">joshpitzalis.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Vasco de Gama
Goa
India
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Web Developer, Freelance
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I help creative entrepreneurs bring ideas to life with simple websites.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
The process of turning an idea into something people can interact with is incredibly fun, as is working with kind people who have the drive to do that sort of thing.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
Much success can come from the repeated application of a single principle: "First, try the dumbest thing that might actually work."
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
